title: Deer Hunter 3 Gold
description: Deer Hunter 3 Gold Edition adds many new features to the already popular and exciting Deer Hunter 3 game--you can even play as the deer and have your online hunting buddies try to track you down. Just as in Deer Hunter 3, the new Gold Edition includes hunting areas that are complete with seasonal changes of the environments, such as leaves falling from the trees, as well as the daily changes of the sun rising and setting. Other environmental effects include fish swimming in lakes and rivers, and animals roaming the hunting areas. Gamers can also save their hunt and pick up where they left off.
